  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 2150d422371cb6340a59202d2ff9a87d, type: 3}
  m_Name: Letter
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::Item
  id: firstLetter
  description: first letter found in the game
  icon: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 55be6f7ab6ac72a4581bcd332e785b5a, type: 3}
  prefab: {fileID: 0}
  itemType: 0
  content: "Dearest Stella, \n\nI\u2019m so glad to hear you\u2019ve learned another
    spell. Your bravery and commitment to learning magic despite the kingdom\u2019s
    ridiculous rules is so inspiring! I wish I were writing with better news, but
    there seems to be a predicament with my garden this week. The flowers haven\u2019t
    grown at all! Would you be able to visit and work some magic on them? I get the
    feeling my precious plants need some more care. I hope your studying with Lucien
    this week goes well. \n\n\nBest, Hazel \nPrincess of the Royal Earth Kingdom "
